      <span class="inline-block bg-yellow-400 text-navy-900 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-black uppercase border-2 border-yellow-400 mb-6" style="box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 #1E3A8A;">
        Lorry Financing Guide
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white mb-6 tracking-tight" style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase;">
        JPJ PUSPAKOM Rules 2024: Financing Compliant Lorry Trucks
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-yellow-400 leading-relaxed mb-8 font-bold">
        Essential guide to JPJ and PUSPAKOM requirements for commercial lorry financing. Learn about 6-month inspections, brake test penalties, and how financing helps meet compliance.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 text-sm text-white">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
