          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 p-6 mb-8">
          <p class="text-navy-900 font-bold mb-0">
            <strong>Quick Summary:</strong> Commercial lorries require PUSPAKOM inspection every 6 months costing RM55-RM75. New 2024 enforcement: 3+ brake test failures trigger automatic JPJ blacklist and road ban. Financing newer, compliant vehicles helps avoid these penalties.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-navy-900 mt-12 mb-6" style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;">Understanding JPJ & PUSPAKOM Compliance</h2>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          For logistics operators in Malaysia, maintaining JPJ (Road Transport Department) and PUSPAKOM compliance is non-negotiable. These regulations ensure road safety and vehicle worthiness for commercial operations.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Since <strong>August 31, 2024</strong>, PUSPAKOM's monopoly has ended, opening vehicle inspection to qualified competitors. This change aims to improve service quality and potentially reduce costs for operators.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-navy-900 mt-10 mb-4">What is PUSPAKOM?</h3>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          PUSPAKOM is Malaysia's authorized vehicle inspection center. For commercial lorries, they conduct mandatory inspections to ensure:
        </p>

        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Roadworthiness and safety standards</li>
          <li>Proper load capacity compliance</li>
          <li>Emissions standards adherence</li>
          <li>Structural integrity of commercial vehicles</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-navy-900 mt-12 mb-6" style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;">Mandatory 6-Month PUSPAKOM Inspections</h2>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Commercial lorries must undergo PUSPAKOM inspection <strong>every 6 months</strong> without exception. This requirement applies to:
        </p>

        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>All goods-carrying vehicles (lorries, trucks)</li>
          <li>Prime movers and trailers</li>
          <li>Commercial vans with loaded weight >3.5 tons</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-400 p-6 mb-8">
          <p class="text-navy-900 font-bold mb-0">
            <strong>Inspection Cost:</strong> RM55-RM75 per inspection. Updated Commercial Vehicle (Goods) Inspection Guidelines were released in June 2024.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-navy-900 mt-12 mb-6" style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;">Brake Test Penalty: The 3-Strike Rule</h2>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          The most critical enforcement in 2024 affects brake testing:
        </p>

        <div class="bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-400 p-6 mb-8">
          <h4 class="text-red-900 font-black text-lg mb-3">NEW: Brake Test Blacklist Rule</h4>
          <ul class="text-red-900 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>3+ Failed Brake Tests</strong> = Automatic JPJ Blacklist</li>
            <li>JPJ notification triggers immediate road ban</li>
            <li>Vehicle prohibited from operation until compliance</li>
            <li>Financial losses from downtime and re-inspection</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          <em>Financing Solution:</em> Newer lorries with modern braking systems significantly reduce failure risk. When financing through Ing Heng Credit, we help you select vehicles that meet current PUSPAKOM standards.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-navy-900 mt-12 mb-6" style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;">Required Documentation for Commercial Lorries</h2>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          To operate a commercial lorry legally and qualify for financing, you need these documents:
        </p>

        <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
          <table class="w-full border-collapse border-2 border-navy-900">
            <thead>
              <tr class="bg-navy-900 text-white">
                <th class="p-4 text-left font-bold border border-navy-900">Document</th>
                <th class="p-4 text-left font-bold border border-navy-900">Description</th>
                <th class="p-4 text-left font-bold border border-navy-900">Priority</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              {requiredDocs.map((doc, index) => (
                <tr class={index % 2 === 0 ? 'bg-white' : 'bg-gray-50'}>
                  <td class="p-4 border border-gray-300 font-bold">{doc.doc}</td>
                  <td class="p-4 border border-gray-300">{doc.description}</td>
                  <td class="p-4 border border-gray-300">
                    <span class={`inline-block px-3 py-1 text-xs font-bold ${
                      doc.priority === 'Mandatory' ? 'bg-red-100 text-red-800' :
                      'bg-blue-100 text-blue-800'
                    }`}>
                      {doc.priority}
                    </span>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              ))}
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-navy-900 mt-12 mb-6" style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;">PUSPAKOM Inspection Checklist</h2>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          During your 6-month inspection, PUSPAKOM checks these critical areas:
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8">
          {inspectionChecks.map((item) => (
            <div class="border-2 border-gray-200 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">{item.check}</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">{item.details}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 p-6 mb-8">
          <h4 class="text-navy-900 font-black text-lg mb-3">Financing Tip</h4>
          <p class="text-navy-900 mb-0">
            When financing a lorry, ask for the PUSPAKOM inspection history. Vehicles with consistent pass records are better investments and less likely to face downtime from compliance issues.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-navy-900 mt-12 mb-6" style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;">JPJ Commercial Vehicle License Renewal</h2>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Commercial vehicle licenses follow different renewal rules compared to private vehicles:
        </p>

        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>First 2 years:</strong> Maximum 1-year renewal period</li>
          <li><strong>After 2 years:</strong> Maximum 6-month renewal period</li>
          <li><strong>Required:</strong> Valid PUSPAKOM inspection for each renewal</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          This means commercial lorries essentially require biannual inspections and license renewals, doubling the administrative burden compared to private vehicles.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-navy-900 mt-12 mb-6" style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;">PUSPAKOM Monopoly Ends: What Changed?</h2>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Effective <strong>August 31, 2024</strong>, PUSPAKOM's concession ended. The government now allows qualified competitors to provide vehicle inspection services:
        </p>

        <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-400 p-6 mb-8">
          <h4 class="text-green-900 font-black text-lg mb-3">Benefits for Operators</h4>
          <ul class="text-green-900 space-y-2">
            <li>Potential cost reduction through competition</li>
            <li>Improved service quality and faster turnaround</li>
            <li>More inspection center locations</li>
            <li>Better customer service standards</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          <em>Important:</em> New inspection providers cannot be workshops (must adhere to regulations). This ensures impartial inspection quality.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-navy-900 mt-12 mb-6" style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;">How Lorry Financing Helps with Compliance</h2>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Financing your commercial lorry through Ing Heng Credit offers several compliance advantages:
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-navy-900 mt-10 mb-4">1. Newer Vehicles = Fewer Compliance Issues</h3>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Modern lorries come with advanced braking systems, better structural integrity, and emissions compliance. This reduces PUSPAKOM failure risk and prevents blacklisting.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-navy-900 mt-10 mb-4">2. Structured Maintenance Budget</h3>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Hire purchase installments create predictable monthly expenses, making it easier to budget for biannual inspections, maintenance, and license renewals.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-navy-900 mt-10 mb-4">3. Documentation Support</h3>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          We guide you through the financing application with all required JPJ and PUSPAKOM documentation, ensuring your financed vehicle is fully compliant from day one.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-navy-900 mt-10 mb-4">4. Trade-In Options</h3>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          When your older lorry faces increasing compliance issues, we offer trade-in financing to upgrade to newer, more compliant vehicles with better inspection records.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-navy-900 mt-12 mb-6" style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;">Cost Comparison: Old vs. New Lorries</h2>

        <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
          <table class="w-full border-collapse border-2 border-navy-900">
            <thead>
              <tr class="bg-navy-900 text-white">
                <th class="p-4 text-left font-bold border border-navy-900">Factor</th>
                <th class="p-4 text-left font-bold border border-navy-900">Old Lorry (>10 years)</th>
                <th class="p-4 text-left font-bold border border-navy-900">New Lorry (Financed)</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr class="bg-white">
                <td class="p-4 border border-gray-300 font-bold">Inspection Pass Rate</td>
                <td class="p-4 border border-gray-300">60-70%</td>
                <td class="p-4 border border-gray-300 text-green-700 font-bold">95%+</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-gray-50">
                <td class="p-4 border border-gray-300 font-bold">Brake Test Failures</td>
                <td class="p-4 border border-gray-300 text-red-700">High risk</td>
                <td class="p-4 border border-gray-300 text-green-700 font-bold">Very low risk</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-white">
                <td class="p-4 border border-gray-300 font-bold">Downtime from Repairs</td>
                <td class="p-4 border border-gray-300 text-red-700">Frequent</td>
                <td class="p-4 border border-gray-300 text-green-700 font-bold">Minimal</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-gray-50">
                <td class="p-4 border border-gray-300 font-bold">Resale Value</td>
                <td class="p-4 border border-gray-300 text-red-700">Declining rapidly</td>
                <td class="p-4 border border-gray-300 text-green-700 font-bold">Stable</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-navy-900 mt-12 mb-6" style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;">Why Choose Ing Heng Credit for JPJ-Compliant Lorry Financing?</h2>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div class="card-brutalist p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-navy-900 mb-3">Pre-Approved Vehicle Selection</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">We recommend lorries with strong PUSPAKOM pass records and modern safety features.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-brutalist p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-navy-900 mb-3">Documentation Guidance</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Complete support for JPJ and PUSPAKOM requirements throughout financing.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-brutalist p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-navy-900 mb-3">0% Down Payment Available</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Preserve cash for inspections, licensing, and initial operations.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-brutalist p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-navy-900 mb-3">Fast Approval (72 Hours)</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Minimize downtime and get your compliant lorry on the road quickly.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-navy-900 mt-12 mb-6" style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;">Get Started: JPJ-Compliant Lorry Financing Checklist</h2>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Before applying for commercial lorry financing, prepare:
        </p>

        <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Valid business registration (SSM)</li>
          <li>Existing PUSPAKOM inspection history (if any)</li>
          <li>Financial statements (bank statements, tax returns)</li>
          <li>JPJ license renewal schedule</li>
          <li>APAD permit (for goods transportation)</li>
          <li>Insurance quotation</li>
        </ol>

      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="section bg-gradient-to-r from-navy-900 to-navy-700 text-white">
    <div class="container-custom text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
        Finance a JPJ-Compliant Lorry Today
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-90">
        Avoid brake test blacklists and compliance penalties. Get approved for a new, compliant commercial lorry with 0% down payment options.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
